So far the direct chain is narrow at the mesh layer but wide at `CollisionWorld::canMove`: 
`FloorMesh::pathWalkCircleGetIds` feeds `pathWalkCircle`, then `Floor::canMove`, then both collision 
resolution and general movement/path probes. I’m now expanding from `CollisionWorld::canMove` to 
object types and AI/pathing users.
