The key downstream contact path is confirmed: non-`WalkOk` floor hits become `Contact`s in 
`CollisionResolve::findContactWithFloor`, and those contacts drive slide/rewind. Next I’m checking 
all public callers of `CollisionWorld::canMove`, including game/client AI and path graph code, to 
separate player-only from NPC/creature/vehicle uses.
