codex
The blast radius includes every `SharedCreatureObjectTemplate`, not just the avatar: collision 
properties set `mobile`, pull template collision radius, and allocate a `Footprint`. That covers 
NPCs/creatures/pets and likely mounts/vehicles implemented as creature/mobile templates; path graph 
also uses a 0.5m probe independent of any object.
