Sonnet | make large low-FPS steps behave like retail's small steps (the engine ALREADY sub-steps >2 
m at CollisionWorld.cpp:639 — copy that pattern finer) | root-cause + retail-parity, reuses a PROVEN 
pattern, same semantics finer granularity → low semantic blast. RISK: perf (more canMove 
iterations/frame), and must re-scale `circleHitTime` from sub-step [0,1] to full-frame [0,1]. 
